name: Amethyst // (435 g/mol - 2.660)
description: Amethyst derives from the Greek for "to be intoxicated" and was worn to prevent drunkenness. Promoting love of the divine. Amethyst encourages selflessness and spiritual wisdom. Sleeping with Amethyst Facilitates out-of-body experiences, helps dream recall, and assist visualization. It guards against psychic attack, transmuting it into love. A natural tranquilizer, Amethyst blocks geopathic stress and negative environmental energies.
